### Standings Tests

### 1. TeamStandings ReadList (Legacy) - Empty table
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/TeamStandings.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json

### 2. TeamStandings ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/team-standings/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 3. RealStandings ReadList (Legacy) - By Competition and MatchDay
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/RealStandings.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byCompetition&realCompetitionID={{testRealCompetitionID}}&realCompetitionMatchDay={{testRealCompetitionMatchDay}}

### 4. RealStandings ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/real-standings/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realCompetitionID": {{testRealCompetitionID}},
  "realCompetitionMatchDay": {{testRealCompetitionMatchDay}}
}

### 5. RealStandings ReadList - Filter by SYMID
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/RealStandings.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byCompetition&realCompetitionSYMID=EN_PR&realCompetitionMatchDay=10

### 6. RealTeamStandings ReadList (Legacy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/RealTeamStandings.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byTeam&realCompetitionID={{testRealCompetitionID}}&realTeamID=1

### 7. RealTeamStandings ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/real-team-standings/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realCompetitionID": {{testRealCompetitionID}},
  "realTeamID": 1
}
